text: Don't know about that.  I played FFXI for 3 years through much of the end game content.  It is a VERY ( I emphasize that for a reason) rough game, even after all these years.  Very hard to get caught up on everything, very unforgiving with professions or just doing what you want.  Now, I will say a positive or two was the class system.  I enjoyed being able to do any class on 1 character (although playing catch up was rough and then doing the same zones over and over), atmosphere, and the music.
